parameters: 【Masamune】 This is...

【Tommy】 Looks like a hit. I think the person who
created this space must have hidden some treasure.
【Tommy】 I wish it was a valuable grimoire.
【Sister Freya】 Monsters...

【Leon】 I have plenty of money, so I'll give it to
Masamune.
【Masamune】 That would be helpful...
【Masamune】 It's quite explicit... Hm, this book...
【Tommy】 A grimoire?

【Masamune】 Hmm, it's an old book, but it seems
different.
【Masamune】 Should I give it a read?

Long ago, in a time far before I was born, the
Demon King was secretly summoned.

However, despite being summoned to the surface
through a ritual that required a great sacrifice,
the king distances themselves from the army.

The subordinate demons tried to stop them, but
they dismissed any interest in invading the
surface.

The king has not appeared before the Fly Knights
since then.

Humans were also frightened when they heard rumors
that the king had been summoned, but there is no
sign of them advancing.

And so, as time passed, the existence of the king
was gradually forgotten.
【Masamune】 A novel... and demons appear too.
【Tommy】 What, it's not a grimoire?

【Masamune】 If Tommy doesn't need it, I'll just
take it for now.

【Masamune】 (It doesn't seem to have anything to do
with the person who has Leviathan trapped in this
space.)
【Masamune】 (It was a futile effort...)

【Skeleton Head】 But still, for us to defeat such a
big demon...
【Tommy】 That was amazing, right?
【Leon】 Magic might not be something to throw away.
【Masamune】 (Well, whatever)
